  "displayTitle": "<span class=\"mw-page-title-main\">Caviar</span>",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-content-ltr mw-parser-output\"><p><i>Exclusive to:</i> <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Shipwrecked\" title=\"Shipwrecked\"><img alt=\"Shipwrecked icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Shipwrecked_icon.png/32px-Shipwrecked_icon.png?3f6ffb\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\"></a><br>\n</p>\n\n<p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n\n<p><b>Caviar</b> is a <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Food\" title=\"Food\">Food</a> <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Item\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Item\">Item</a> exclusive to the <i><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Don%27t_Starve:_Shipwrecked\" title=\"Don&#x27;t Starve: Shipwrecked\">Shipwrecked</a></i> DLC. It is cooked in the <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crock_Pot\" title=\"Crock Pot\">Crock Pot</a> by adding 1 <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Vegetable\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Vegetable\">Vegetable</a> and 1 <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Roe\" title=\"Roe\">Roe</a>. Alternatively, 3 <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Roe\" title=\"Roe\">Cooked Roe</a> can be used.\n</p><p>Caviar takes 40 seconds to cook, and restores 3 <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Health\" title=\"Health\"><img alt=\"Health Icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Health_Icon.png/20px-Health_Icon.png?1ec0e6\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"></a>, 12.5 <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Hunger\" title=\"Hunger\"><img alt=\"Hunger Icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Hunger_Icon.png/20px-Hunger_Icon.png?9d0486\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"></a>, and 33 <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Sanity\" title=\"Sanity\"><img alt=\"Sanity Icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Sanity_Icon.png/20px-Sanity_Icon.png?eae728\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"></a> when eaten. Due to its low health and hunger restoration, it&#x27;s best to eat for its high sanity restoration. It can be traded with the <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Yaarctopus\" title=\"Yaarctopus\">Yaarctopus</a> for a <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Bottle_Lantern\" title=\"Bottle Lantern\">Bottle Lantern</a>.\n</p><p><br>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Prerequisites\">Prerequisites</span></h2>\n<ul><li>Requires: <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Roe\" title=\"Roe\"><img alt=\"Roe.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Roe.png?f773e0\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a> or <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Roe\" title=\"Roe\"><img alt=\"Cooked Roe.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Cooked_Roe.png?477da5\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></li>\n<li>Requires: <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Vegetable\" title=\"Vegetable\"><img alt=\"Vegetables Crock Pot.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Vegetables_Crock_Pot.png?fc26f1\" width=\"466\" height=\"130\"></a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recipe\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Cookbook\" title=\"Cookbook\"><img alt=\"Cookbook.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Cookbook.png/32px-Cookbook.png?a6d040\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a> Recipe</span></h2>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Roe\" title=\"Roe\"><img alt=\"Roe.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Roe.png?f773e0\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Vegetables\" title=\"Vegetables\"><img alt=\"Veggie.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Veggie.png?80149d\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Filler\" title=\"Filler\"><img alt=\"Filler.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Filler.png?b5d099\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>×<b>2</b></p></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crock_Pot\" title=\"Crock Pot\"><img alt=\"Crock Pot.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Crock_Pot.png/42px-Crock_Pot.png?8263f1\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Caviar\" title=\"Caviar\"><img alt=\"Caviar.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Caviar.png?44e177\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Cooked_Roe\" title=\"Cooked Roe\"><img alt=\"Cooked Roe.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Cooked_Roe.png?477da5\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>×<b>3</b></p></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Vegetables\" title=\"Vegetables\"><img alt=\"Veggie.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Veggie.png?80149d\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crock_Pot\" title=\"Crock Pot\"><img alt=\"Crock Pot.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Crock_Pot.png/42px-Crock_Pot.png?8263f1\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Caviar\" title=\"Caviar\"><img alt=\"Caviar.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Caviar.png?44e177\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Examples\">Examples</span></h2>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Roe\" title=\"Roe\"><img alt=\"Roe.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Roe.png?f773e0\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Seaweed\" title=\"Seaweed\"><img alt=\"Seaweed.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Seaweed.png?1afce2\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Twigs\" title=\"Twigs\"><img alt=\"Twigs.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Twigs.png?2fb15c\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>×<b>2</b></p></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crock_Pot\" title=\"Crock Pot\"><img alt=\"Crock Pot.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Crock_Pot.png/42px-Crock_Pot.png?8263f1\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Caviar\" title=\"Caviar\"><img alt=\"Caviar.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Caviar.png?44e177\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Roe\" title=\"Roe\"><img alt=\"Roe.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Roe.png?f773e0\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>×<b>2</b></p></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Seaweed\" title=\"Seaweed\"><img alt=\"Seaweed.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Seaweed.png?1afce2\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Twigs\" title=\"Twigs\"><img alt=\"Twigs.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Twigs.png?2fb15c\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crock_Pot\" title=\"Crock Pot\"><img alt=\"Crock Pot.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Crock_Pot.png/42px-Crock_Pot.png?8263f1\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Caviar\" title=\"Caviar\"><img alt=\"Caviar.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Caviar.png?44e177\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Cooked_Roe\" title=\"Cooked Roe\"><img alt=\"Cooked Roe.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Cooked_Roe.png?477da5\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>×<b>3</b></p></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Sweet_Potato\" title=\"Sweet Potato\"><img alt=\"Sweet Potato.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Sweet_Potato.png?8b4bdd\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crock_Pot\" title=\"Crock Pot\"><img alt=\"Crock Pot.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Crock_Pot.png/42px-Crock_Pot.png?8263f1\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Caviar\" title=\"Caviar\"><img alt=\"Caviar.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Caviar.png?44e177\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Roe\" title=\"Roe\"><img alt=\"Roe.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Roe.png?f773e0\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>×<b>2</b></p></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Sweet_Potato\" title=\"Sweet Potato\"><img alt=\"Sweet Potato.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Sweet_Potato.png?8b4bdd\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Mandrake\" title=\"Mandrake\"><img alt=\"Mandrake.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Mandrake.png?c94a2f\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crock_Pot\" title=\"Crock Pot\"><img alt=\"Crock Pot.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Crock_Pot.png/42px-Crock_Pot.png?8263f1\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Caviar\" title=\"Caviar\"><img alt=\"Caviar.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Caviar.png?44e177\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Trivia\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Placeholder\" title=\"Placeholder\"><img alt=\"Placeholder.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Placeholder.png/32px-Placeholder.png?210282\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a> Trivia</span></h2>\n<ul><li>Caviar was added to the <i>Shipwrecked</i> DLC more than a year after its official completion in the <i><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Don%27t_Starve:_Shipwrecked#November_21st,_2017_-_Home_Sea_Home_Update\" title=\"Don&#x27;t Starve: Shipwrecked\">Home Sea Home</a></i> update, after being tested in a beta branch for several months.</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Gallery\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Blueprint\" title=\"Blueprint\"><img alt=\"Blueprint.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Blueprint.png/32px-Blueprint.png?80b6b5\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a> Gallery</span></h2>\n<ul class=\"gallery mw-gallery-traditional\">\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:DS_Shipwrecked_Home_Sea_Home_Update.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Caviar as seen in the poster for the Home Sea Home update.\"><img alt=\"Caviar as seen in the poster for the Home Sea Home update.\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/DS_Shipwrecked_Home_Sea_Home_Update.png/120px-DS_Shipwrecked_Home_Sea_Home_Update.png?9f2ef1\" width=\"120\" height=\"68\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\">Caviar as seen in the poster for the <i><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Don%27t_Starve:_Shipwrecked#November_21,_2017_-_Home_Sea_Home_Update\" title=\"Don&#x27;t Starve: Shipwrecked\">Home Sea Home</a></i> update.</div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"tabber tabber--init\"><a class=\"tabber__tab\" id=\"By_Type-0-label\" href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Caviar#By_Type-0\">By Type</a><a class=\"tabber__tab\" id=\"By_Crock_Pot_Value-0-label\" href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Caviar#By_Crock_Pot_Value-0\">By Crock Pot Value</a><section class=\"tabber__section\"><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n<p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n<p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p></section></div>\n\n\n\n\n</div>",
